# Ignore everything by default
*

# Track only config files
# Note: settings.json is tracked but holds some machine-specific paths
# (e.g. permission globs) that differ between Windows and macOS — review
# those on a new machine.
!.gitignore
!README.md
!CLAUDE.md
!settings.json
!rules/
!rules/**

# Track user-authored Claude Code config directories
!skills/
!skills/**
!agents/
!agents/**
!commands/
!commands/**
